    "intro": "Interpretation moves from what the text says to what it means — tracing the author's intent in its original context and following the canonical thread that runs from David's personal confession through the Messiah's resurrection to the believer's eternal hope. The movements below follow the psalm's own argument, supplementing with Hebrew notes where the language materially sharpens the meaning.",
